{"id": "versterk-inkoopvoorwaarden-met-nis2-clausules__c4-paragraph__0002", "text": "[Cybersecurity](https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/veilig/index.html)", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "versterk-inkoopvoorwaarden-met-nis2-clausules__c4-paragraph__0002", "source_slug": "versterk-inkoopvoorwaarden-met-nis2-clausules", "source_title": "Strengthen purchasing conditions with NIS2 clauses", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/versterk-inkoopvoorwaarden-met-nis2-clausules.html", "source_date": "2025-10-06", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 2, "n_chunks_total": 12, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "versterk-inkoopvoorwaarden-met-nis2-clausules__c4-paragraph__0003", "text": "The NIS2 guideline places high demands on organizations and their suppliers. This European law obliges companies to improve their digital resilience. If a supplier does not meet cybersecurity requirements, your company can still be held responsible. It is therefore important to record clear agreements in the purchasing conditions.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "versterk-inkoopvoorwaarden-met-nis2-clausules__c4-paragraph__0003", "source_slug": "versterk-inkoopvoorwaarden-met-nis2-clausules", "source_title": "Strengthen purchasing conditions with NIS2 clauses", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/versterk-inkoopvoorwaarden-met-nis2-clausules.html", "source_date": "2025-10-06", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 3, "n_chunks_total": 12, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "versterk-inkoopvoorwaarden-met-nis2-clausules__c4-paragraph__0004", "text": "With clear purchasing conditions you determine what you expect from suppliers. For example, about information security and risk management. This reduces the chance of misunderstandings and accelerates the preparation for NIS2. This way you prevent problems towards the deadline in 2026.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "versterk-inkoopvoorwaarden-met-nis2-clausules__c4-paragraph__0004", "source_slug": "versterk-inkoopvoorwaarden-met-nis2-clausules", "source_title": "Strengthen purchasing conditions with NIS2 clauses", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/versterk-inkoopvoorwaarden-met-nis2-clausules.html", "source_date": "2025-10-06", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 4, "n_chunks_total": 12, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "versterk-inkoopvoorwaarden-met-nis2-clausules__c4-paragraph__0005", "text": "Not every company has the time or expertise to write legal texts themselves. That is why Samen Digitaal Veilig offers [a free sample text](https://samendigitaalveilig.nl/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250207-Model-addendum-inkoop-supply-chain-NIS2.pdf) together with NEVI. You can include these in contracts, quotations or existing purchasing documents.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "versterk-inkoopvoorwaarden-met-nis2-clausules__c4-paragraph__0005", "source_slug": "versterk-inkoopvoorwaarden-met-nis2-clausules", "source_title": "Strengthen purchasing conditions with NIS2 clauses", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/versterk-inkoopvoorwaarden-met-nis2-clausules.html", "source_date": "2025-10-06", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 5, "n_chunks_total": 12, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "versterk-inkoopvoorwaarden-met-nis2-clausules__c4-paragraph__0006", "text": "Including NIS2 clauses in the purchasing conditions helps with legal compliance. You don't just strengthen your own organization. You also contribute to a safer digital ecosystem.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "versterk-inkoopvoorwaarden-met-nis2-clausules__c4-paragraph__0006", "source_slug": "versterk-inkoopvoorwaarden-met-nis2-clausules", "source_title": "Strengthen purchasing conditions with NIS2 clauses", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/versterk-inkoopvoorwaarden-met-nis2-clausules.html", "source_date": "2025-10-06", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 6, "n_chunks_total": 12, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "versterk-inkoopvoorwaarden-met-nis2-clausules__c4-paragraph__0007", "text": "This article was produced in collaboration with [Samen Digitaal Veilig](https://www.samendigitaalveilig.nl/).", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "versterk-inkoopvoorwaarden-met-nis2-clausules__c4-paragraph__0007", "source_slug": "versterk-inkoopvoorwaarden-met-nis2-clausules", "source_title": "Strengthen purchasing conditions with NIS2 clauses", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/versterk-inkoopvoorwaarden-met-nis2-clausules.html", "source_date": "2025-10-06", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 7, "n_chunks_total": 12, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "versterk-inkoopvoorwaarden-met-nis2-clausules__c4-paragraph__0008", "text": "About 1 in 5 entrepreneurs is confronted with cybercrime. Such a cyber incident can have major consequences for business operations, customers, suppliers or reputation. Taking appropriate measures is therefore important for every company.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "versterk-inkoopvoorwaarden-met-nis2-clausules__c4-paragraph__0008", "source_slug": "versterk-inkoopvoorwaarden-met-nis2-clausules", "source_title": "Strengthen purchasing conditions with NIS2 clauses", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/versterk-inkoopvoorwaarden-met-nis2-clausules.html", "source_date": "2025-10-06", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 8, "n_chunks_total": 12, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "versterk-inkoopvoorwaarden-met-nis2-clausules__c4-paragraph__0009", "text": "- Do you have an SME company and do you want to reduce your cyber risks? Then take a look at [Cyber ​​Fundament](https://doorpassen.abnamro.nl/producten-en-diensten/cyber-voor-het-mkb/), especially for SME entrepreneurs.\n- Learn more about the 4-in-1 cyber solution [Cyber ​​Safe & Secure](https://doorpassen.abnamro.nl/producten-en-diensten/cyber-veilig-en-zeker/?icmp=cm-od_article-insights_btn-link) especially for large businesses and reduce your cyber risks.\n- Do you also want to [do business safely](https://doorpassen.abnamro.nl/producten-en-diensten/veilig-ondernemen/?icmp=cm-od_article-insights_btn-link)? View smart tools, useful articles and cyber webinars.\n- [Report fraud to us](https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/prive/abnamro/veilig-banken/fraude-melden.html \"Report fraud\"), even if in doubt, after which our helpdesk will help you immediately.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "versterk-inkoopvoorwaarden-met-nis2-clausules__c4-paragraph__0009", "source_slug": "versterk-inkoopvoorwaarden-met-nis2-clausules", "source_title": "Strengthen purchasing conditions with NIS2 clauses", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/versterk-inkoopvoorwaarden-met-nis2-clausules.html", "source_date": "2025-10-06", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 9, "n_chunks_total": 12, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
